# .hermes: 두뇌 구조(SOUL/config/profile/.env.template)만 추적, 시크릿(.env/auth.json)·런타임(db/sessions/memories/logs/cache)은 제외
.hermes/*
!.hermes/profiles/
.hermes/profiles/*/*
!.hermes/profiles/*/SOUL.md
!.hermes/profiles/*/config.yaml
!.hermes/profiles/*/profile.yaml
!.hermes/profiles/*/.env.template

.claude/
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
**/worktrees/
**/node_modules/
workspace/invest/data/
*.log
